commitmsg: Add deployment information to README.
Tweaks to mid-sized screen CSS.
Store API responses in memcached for a short time to prevent rate limiting.
Adds a default condensed view of each Podio item.
Prepare for Heroku deployment.
Adds ability to sort/filter roadmap items.

Tweaks for mobile:
* Add a viewport tag
* Absolutely position the throbber's bits.
Tweak stacking order on mobile.
Tweak mobile spacing.
Hide footer while throbber is shown, tweak throbber animation and timing.
Use that beautiful favicon jug.
Correctly retrieve Podio item ID.
Add Throbber component to smooth page transitions.
Styles <ol>s inside of BlockText components.
Remove quotes from LinkItem href attribute.
Link to the correct code repository.
Do not render BlockText components with falsy text values.
Allow configuration to be loaded from a local file.
Require the correct Html component in the server.
Appropriately use .jsx and .js.

Reorganize the code a bit:
- Remove the unused Page component and PageStore.
- Move Podio-related components into their own directory.
A little bit of front-end cleanup.
Wires up On Deck and Roadmap handlers.
Wires up Activity handler.
Adds bare-bones service to get activity data, wires up to activity view.
Adds API endpoints to server.
Import assets from original Jugband application.
Initial commit; bootstrapped application.
